{"tid":33851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《經濟》引述梁營：梁振英連任辦開始運作","createTime":"2016-12-11T05:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T10:14:33.000Z","uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5413b5d71f80cb597ca413052cec676f3a058afc","tid":33851,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:56:30.000Z","msg":"《經濟日報》政情專欄傅流螢今日引述「梁營中人」指出，特首梁振英的連任辦已開始運作，並已進行拉票工作。梁振英於新社聯的安排下，本月兩度到訪新界會見地區人士，據悉他短期內於民建聯安排下將到訪九龍西。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報道梁振英周日（11月27日）及下周日（12月4日）會分別到觀塘及深水埗出席交流會，上屆競選特首時「一枝筆、一本簿、一張摺凳」再次出現，周日到觀塘是應「大專青年協會」的邀請，創辦人正是民建聯觀塘區議員張琪騰。至於到深水埗落區，報道指出，同樣是當區的民建聯區議員安排。<br />\n<br />\n報道提到，新民黨在在選舉委員會選舉後三天後將舉行特別會員大會，到時新民黨主席葉劉會就參選特首尋求會員意見及支持，但究竟會否正式宣布參選，暫時未有定案。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，新民黨領導層換班的問題，成為了葉劉部署特首選戰前的重要考慮，由於葉、田北辰兩人今年都已66歲，最多只會做多一屆議員，葉劉最近正積極游說獨立議員，如謝偉俊加盟該黨，為該黨接班鋪路。"},{"pid":"e5c57a8bc4a97eeeb86054f27d3149a3ce9c3a2a","tid":33851,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"梁粉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78157ffc53ea986216bbc42e9836feeb59dd1a6","tid":33851,"uid":56704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"有時候真係忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f01ccb45ca2954bf8a4bc0065cbe639a45d35d1","tid":33851,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61129a9e417f9c7298bc90469a92f4d85eb444a3","tid":33851,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時候真係忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63755045d52286c4ccfbfa1f46f997bd2d5d502f","tid":33851,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"我信佢寫既野<br />\n因為689應該都係突然被dq"},{"pid":"d8fc5432b65644aa8f459432c619715108997b64","tid":33851,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/181425_a236e6917655cd752c070571a45ba531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F181425_a236e6917655cd752c070571a45ba531.jpg&h=5ccf7e4b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}